    "answer_en": "A challenge could be ensuring consistent compliance with the regulations.  We need to be vigilant about monitoring and enforcing those standards. Another potential issue is the cost of registration and accreditation – ensuring we’re getting the best possible rates and understanding the financial implications.  We can mitigate this by working closely with the NFRC to understand their fee structures and explore potential support programs.  Also, we need to be proactive in identifying and addressing any loopholes or inconsistencies in the regulations."
  },
  {
