    "question_en": "I want to improve the quality of my maize. What are some techniques for improving the taste and nutritional value of the crop?",
    "answer_en": "Focus on proper planting spacing, fertilization, and soil management.  Consider using cover crops to improve soil structure and nutrient retention.  Also, ensure you're providing adequate water and sunlight.  Do you have access to any post-harvest processing techniques to enhance the quality of your maize?"
  },
